    "Teams can engage GenAI in brainstorming sessions to generate ideas for process improvements during retrospectives.",
    " Dynamic Prioritization and Answering Questions on Backlog Items: GenAI can dynamically prioritize backlog items based on changing requirements, user feedback, and business priorities.",
